Pages in the breadcrumbs is confusing as it's the same name in every space, but it's a space-specific page. It is taking up valuable real estate in the Breadcrumbs. How do I remove it so the first line in Breadcrumbs is the space name?
We have multiple spaces in our instance and it's important each user knows which space they are in. Not all users have access to the spaces so when a user shares, the first thing they need to know is what space they are in.
Adding 'Pages' to the breadcrumbs has increased confusion and reduced usability for us. Please tell me how to make it go away.

